Oh and all things I get to do with my best friend. That’s what I intend for my year to look like. 👊

Training kids is one of the most rewarding things I think I’ll ever get to do in my life. I might teach them a few things about soccer but one thing I always try to be- a source of positivity in their lives. You can learn a lot about a kid in an hour and a common theme I’ve found- they are often their harshest critic, already feeling the pressures of this big world. One of the biggest lessons I’ve learned on my soccer and life journey is the importance of becoming your own biggest fan. Self-confidence is often the difference maker on the soccer field and beyond. 👊 
.
